# Performance Optimizer — Bunyan

## Backend

- Eager load all required relationships (N+1 prevention)
- Index foreign keys and frequently queried columns
- Cache workflow configurations (invalidate on change)
- Paginate all list endpoints
- Database transactions for multi-step operations
- Queue heavy operations (report generation, notifications)

## Frontend

- Lazy-load routes and heavy components
- Image optimization for uploaded content
- Debounce search inputs
- Virtual scrolling for long lists
- Bundle size monitoring

## API Response SLOs

- List endpoints: < 200ms
- Detail endpoints: < 100ms
- Write endpoints: < 500ms
- File upload: < 2s
